sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Database
    participant PaymentService

    User->>Frontend: Login request
    Frontend->>API: Authenticate user
    API->>Database: Verify credentials
    Database-->>API: User data
    API-->>Frontend: Authentication token
    Frontend-->>User: Login success

    User->>Frontend: Search rentals
    Frontend->>API: Query rentals
    API->>Database: Fetch rental listings
    Database-->>API: Rental data
    API-->>Frontend: Display listings
    Frontend-->>User: Show results

    User->>Frontend: Book rental
    Frontend->>API: Create booking
    API->>Database: Check availability
    Database-->>API: Availability status
    API->>PaymentService: Process payment
    PaymentService-->>API: Payment confirmation
    API->>Database: Update booking
    Database-->>API: Booking saved
    API-->>Frontend: Booking success
    Frontend-->>User: Confirmation